{"tid":2070409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李兆波料本港明年或面臨破產高峰期","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T06:20:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48e94b2e8a24fbaedbdc6de3992b226f253cc48e","tid":2070409,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532968-20200619.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532968-20200619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C3qIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=9fc7f35d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532968-20200619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ac439170\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532968-20200619.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府數據顯示，上月提交破產呈請書有2079宗，首5個月逾3600宗，按年升近13%。<br />\n<br />\n中文大學商學院高級講師李兆波表示，受到疫情影響，預計破產宗數將會持續增加，由於數據滯後，加上疫情持續，預計明年才是破產高峰期，加上疫情可能反覆，破產宗數有機會達2萬宗。而2003年沙士時有近2.5萬宗破產。<br />\n<br />\n對於有報道指，政府或引入破產保護令法定公司救助程序。他指若屬實是好事，令企業可渡過最惡劣時間。"},{"pid":"2004f6d3c8c81482703e1a43ebadf10761ae8b83","tid":2070409,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"留字等睇黑心兒登仔幸災樂禍"}]}